	   <tr><td colspan=2>I think she must spawn faster than she used to, because after killing her once (dropped the robe) two magicians spawned five minutes later, and Najena popped about 10 minutes after we killed them.  I actually hadto wait much longer for Rathyl to spawn, waited for 20 minutes before a couple of magicians spawned, he spawned about 15 minutes after that.  Luckily, she dropped the book the second time.  She also dropped dark elf parts, which I believe is a random drop off any dark elf NPC.<br><br>Najena seems to be a rather empty dungeon now, never seen more than 5 people in their at once, most camping itms for the magician epic.  Some page is a rare random drop off the magicians.  Only a handful of people are ever after Najena herself.<br>&nbsp;<br>Troodon, AKA Zararazu, Level 38 Iksar Monk, Jaggedpine Defender, Solusek Ro</td></tr>
